text: Hellinsia madecasseus is a moth of the family Pterophoridae. ==Distribution== It is known from the Democratic Republic of Congo, Madagascar, Tanzania, South Africa and Malawi.Kovtunovich, Ustejuzhanin & Murphy, 2014.Plume moths of Malawi (Lepidoptera: Pterophoridae).
